The main usage to be tracked is gaming, and it is done using a

Playnite has export plugin to csv, in future this app can accept

Estimates RoI of any Item or at Build level
A GPU may be used in several builds, each occurrence may play
several games. Same game with multiple GPU on same system
should result in two entries in Game Stats. In Playnite too, we can
do it by suffixing the Name with GPU
Items supported would be GPU and Controllers - these are likely
to be swapped in multiple builds, and directly impact gameplay.
Other hardware components need not be considered and would
unnecessarily make the soution too complex to maintain.
This page should take the input of a GPU or controller, then list all
games and a total amount of hours played.
At least one RAM and Storage are required, rest olive boxes are optional. All off-white boxes are required
